 of time and creation, Lord Brahma. This powerful moniker can serve as an inspiration for personal growth and recognition, inspiring feelings of pride and self-worth.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4\",\"children\":\"In Hindu spirituality, the name \\\"Aajad\\\" is revered as a connection to Lord Brahma, the creator and sustainer of the universe. It's believed that an individual carrying this name is imbued with the divine qualities of creation, growth, and development, just like the deity himself. Thus, the name offers a spiritual foundation that encompasses both creativity and personal transformation.\"}],\"$undefined\",null,\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"$L3c\",null,{\"className\":\"my-6\",\"minHeight\":\"90px\",\"instanceId\":\"name-detail-mid\"}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"nv-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$21:props:children:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-clock h-5 w-5\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\",\"children\":\"Historical Usage\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Historical References\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\",\"children\":\"Historical records show that Aajad was a king of the Chera Dynasty in the 10th century AD. The nam